fields.title: La Luna
fields.review: La Luna is a good short film with a great story and humor.

fields.title: The Devil's Backbone
fields.review: In a nutshell, 'El Espinazo Del Diablo' is a horrifying, tragic but beautiful film.

fields.title: Return of the Tooth Fairy
fields.review: What we have is a tiresome rethread of every ghostly/imaginary monster/demonic story ever told in a painfully slow way.

fields.title: The Boss Baby: Family Business
fields.review: Fun film for kids. Definitely not as good as the first film.

fields.title: Batman: Bad Blood
fields.review: A lot of these animated superhero features have a lot of cool stuff in them, but Batman: Bad Blood just lacked stuff that make you go: awesome!

fields.title: The Worst Week Of My Life
fields.review: After a few reels, just the day captions get a laugh. Throw in great looking women to flank unshaven De Luigi.

fields.title: Upgrade
fields.review: A classic to remember. Look forward to seeing this again.

fields.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
fields.review: Watch it and believe me, you'll get hooked!

fields.title: Winter Sleep
fields.review: Winter Sleep is a masterpiece by Nuri Bilge Ceylan, a film shining with literary eloquence and incisive social criticism.

fields.title: Azur & Asmar: The Princes' Quest
fields.review: It may seem curious but the word that I voiced when it ended was DELICIOUS. There are so many impacting images that linger even now in my mind's eye.
